result.name: Adventureland

reviews.text: Adventureland is great place to go with your family . It has attractions like Tarzan's Treehouse and  Jungle River Cruise. You can also enjoy the live shows in the 'Theatre in the Wild'.

If you are a nature lover and enjoy scenic locations, then you'll surely love it here. There are several rides in which you can take in this place. Namely the river cruise which you can choose which language that you want for the ride: English, Cantonese or  Manderin. It takes a bit of waiting for this ride but the adventure sort of surprised me in between. You'll see animals and ... Other things too. (No spoilers). Besides that, you can visit Tarzan's  live sized tree house. It's fun of memories and several interactive scenes that makes you engaged with the 'history' of Tarzan. Oh and don't forget the Lion King live show. It's like a musical of the movie, only shorter and sometimes a bit choppy but overall nice to watch. Take a really long wait to see it though.
This place was awesome! A very family friendly place where you could enjoy shows as well as rides. It was the first place I went to while in disneyland.
Most amazing ride i ever had . I just love this place . The boat ride was amazing.
The shows were amazing, especially the 'Festival of the Lion King'! It's a must-see for all ages. The Moana show was great and entertaining, too. 👍
